metadata.name: spring
metadata.description:
This illustration is the first work of the "Four Seasons" collection.

In this collection, we upload works that make use of the emotions of the four seasons!
It starts with spring and ends with winter.

The first start is in spring when the cherry blossoms are in full bloom.
Spring is short, but the pink scenery is very beautiful.



And, we're giving away a small gift to every bidder for this collection :D
Thanks you!
